    %p
      Most excellent!
      %br
      You can review mentors you've favorited
      %br
      from your home screen.
      = image_tag "cflogo.png", {alt: "Codefellows Logo", class: "goHome"}
  %section.popBox.contact
    %p
      Would you like to introduce
      %br
      yourself to Iron Man?
    %button.yesIntro yeah!
    %button.noIntro maybe later
  %section.popMessage.contact
    %p
      Great!
      %br
      We've sent Iron Man an email
      %br
      saying how awesome you are.
      %br
      Keep an eye on your inbox.
    = image_tag "cflogo.png", {alt: "Codefellows Logo", class: "goHome"}
